## Application Variables

| Variable | Description | Default | Required |
|----------|-------------|---------|----------|
| `{{APP_PREFIX}}_APP_NAME` | Application display name | `{{APP_DISPLAY_NAME}}` | No |
| `{{APP_PREFIX}}_APP_ENV` | Environment (development/production) | `development` | No |
